AVERTRONICS INC (3597)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 12.20% to NT$45,682,000 from NT$52,027,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales             45,682           52,027    
YOY%             -12.20%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            245,507          326,788    
YOY%             -24.87% 
=================================================================
 